## Quick start

```bash
# 1. Edit .env if needed (HF_TOKEN, ports, paths).
# 2. Bring it up.
docker compose up -d

# 3. Tail logs until you see "Application startup complete".
docker compose logs -f vllm

# 4. Smoke test it.
pip install openai
python test_client.py
```

The OpenAI-compatible API will be live at `http://localhost:8000/v1`.

