{% if quantization == "bitsandbytes" %}## Custom Dockerfile (BitsAndBytes)

The official `vllm/vllm-openai` image does not include BitsAndBytes. Build a one-line custom image:

```dockerfile
ARG VLLM_IMAGE={{ image_tag }}
FROM ${VLLM_IMAGE}
RUN uv pip install --system "bitsandbytes>=0.49.2"
```

Then change `image:` in `docker-compose.yml` to your built tag and run `docker compose up -d --build`.
